---
---
<section class="section our-story">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">How It All Began</h2>
    <div class="story-body">
      <p>
        Your love story goes here — how you met, the proposal, and
        everything in between. This section will be personalised with your
        own words and photos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .our-story {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .story-body {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .story-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
